{"tid":2123953,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"對國家好失望，又向邪惡美國獻媚！","createTime":"2020-07-25T05:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-25T12:08:32.000Z","uid":23707,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0753a21fc72bc2c926b1833af73d7681a19e4f76","tid":2123953,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:01:08.000Z","msg":"【總領事曾揚言不關　中國駐侯斯頓領館人員終在限期前撤離　美國官員爆門進入】<br />\n<br />\n報道全文：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2OSgeLl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OSgeLl&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxeL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=50baf7c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2OSgeLl</a><br />\n<br />\n美國早前下令中國 72 小時內關閉中國駐侯斯頓領事館，限期在當地時間週五（24 日）下午 4 時屆滿。中國駐侯斯頓總領事蔡偉曾經揚言不理會限期，會跟人員繼續留守，惟總領事館工作人員最終都趕及在限期屆滿之前執拾物品離開，國旗和國徽都已經移除。<br />\n<br />\n大約 100 名反中示威者在總領事館外示威，又在總領事館工作人員將物品搬離時搖旗。限期屆滿不久，工作人員就登上私家車離開。在限期屆滿之後，一批工人隨即以電動工具強行開啟總領事館的後門，全程有國務院人員監督，期間他們都沒有回應記者提問。<br />\n<br />\n中國駐侯斯頓總領事蔡偉發表公開信，批評美方單方面挑起事端，蓄意破壞中美關係。蔡偉表示，歷史的前進方向雖然有時會受到少數人的干擾而出現曲折，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">但中美人民友誼不會中斷，中美友好合作的光明前景，任何人都不能阻擋。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccfc0aa981f6c2856fd51ba2f4cf4e343505f271","tid":2123953,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-25T05:03:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4339e76ff7383978f3acd1f991cb